            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/2544-iwxpesy2925032.jpg?VersionId=OqoZUUy3ku80jWFIbijLVcUcaC476Pg_&amp;itok=irA81qSJ" title="位于美国首都华盛顿的中国驻美大使馆（中国驻美大使馆官网档案照）" alt="位于美国首都华盛顿的中国驻美大使馆（中国驻美大使馆官网档案照）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-06/2544-iwxpesy2925032.jpg?VersionId=OqoZUUy3ku80jWFIbijLVcUcaC476Pg_&amp;itok=irA81qSJ" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
